    <item>
      <title>What is the future of the Philippines?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details id=&#34;note&#34; class=&#34;pl-6 pr-4 pb-4 mt-4 mb-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded toc&#34; open&gt;&#xA;  &lt;summary class=&#34;flex items-center font-bold py-2 cursor-pointer justify-between select-none text-black dark:text-white&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;text-xs tracking-wide&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; class=&#34;icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-chevron-down&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;        &lt;polyline points=&#34;6 9 12 15 18 9&#34;&gt;&lt;/polyline&gt;&#xA;     &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;text-sm&#34;&gt;&#xA;    This is an  English Translation of Filipinas Dentro De Cien Años by Jose Rizal&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- Filipinas Dentro De Cien Años (Estudio Politico-Social), by José Rizal &#xA;&#xA;Published in La Solidaridad Sept 1889-Jan 1890&#xA;&#xA;Ahora reimpreso por primera vez. Año de 1905.  --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- Following our custom of approaching directly the most difficult and delicate questions related to the Philippines, without caring about the consequences that our frankness could cause us, we are going in this article to deal with its future. --&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To read the destiny of peoples, we should look at their past.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Will the Philippines Continue as a Spanish colony?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-2/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-2/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details id=&#34;note&#34; class=&#34;pl-6 pr-4 pb-4 mt-4 mb-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded toc&#34; open&gt;&#xA;  &lt;summary class=&#34;flex items-center font-bold py-2 cursor-pointer justify-between select-none text-black dark:text-white&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;text-xs tracking-wide&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; class=&#34;icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-chevron-down&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;        &lt;polyline points=&#34;6 9 12 15 18 9&#34;&gt;&lt;/polyline&gt;&#xA;     &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;text-sm&#34;&gt;&#xA;    This is an  English Translation of Filipinas Dentro De Cien Años by Jose Rizal&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- What will become of the Philippines in a century?  --&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;will-the-philippines-continue-as-a-spanish-colony&#34;&gt;Will the Philippines Continue as a Spanish colony?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If this were asked 300 years ago, when, at the death of Legazpi, the Filipino Malays began little by little to become disillusioned, and finding the yoke heavy they tried in vain to shake it off, no doubt the answer would have been easy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Peaceful Struggles</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-3/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-3/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;English Translation of Filipinas Dentro De Cien Años by Jose Rizal&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- La Solaridad; núm. 18: Barcelona, 31 octubre 1889.  --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- ## 3 --&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Part 2 showed that if the Philippines is to stay under Spain, its politics must change as demanded by Filipinos. &lt;!-- transform themselves in a political sense, as the course of their history and the needs of their inhabitants so demand.  --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>The Qualities of a Filipino</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-3b/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-3b/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;English Translation of Filipinas Dentro De Cien Años by Jose Rizal&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;racial-looks&#34;&gt;Racial Looks&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Each race has its own aesthetics.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;China has 414 million people and has a very ancient civilization. It finds all Europeans ugly, calling them Fan-Kwai or red devils.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Will the Philippines Continue as a Spanish colony?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-4/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-4/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;English Translation of Filipinas Dentro De Cien Años by Jose Rizal&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- IV.  --&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;History does not record &lt;!-- in its annals --&gt; any lasting domination exercised by one people over another, of different races, of strange uses and customs, and of opposing or divergent ideals.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>European Colonial Policy</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-4b/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/writers/rizal/dentro/part-4b/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details id=&#34;note&#34; class=&#34;pl-6 pr-4 pb-4 mt-4 mb-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded toc&#34; open&gt;&#xA;  &lt;summary class=&#34;flex items-center font-bold py-2 cursor-pointer justify-between select-none text-black dark:text-white&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;text-xs tracking-wide&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; class=&#34;icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-chevron-down&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;        &lt;polyline points=&#34;6 9 12 15 18 9&#34;&gt;&lt;/polyline&gt;&#xA;     &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;text-sm&#34;&gt;&#xA;    This is an  English Translation of Filipinas Dentro De Cien Años by Jose Rizal&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;No sensible nation neglects the immense, virgin, unexploited and little-defended continental territories &lt;!-- that the Black Continent offers it --&gt; in order to gain a handful of poor and hardened islands.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
